Ranger Help for: tap stone
===========================

SYNTAX:      rtap
USAGE:       mountain,underground
SLOT COST:   6
BASE SP:     NA
SKILL TYPE:  religious

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to tap into the deep energy of the earth
through stone, restoring spell points. The Ranger places a hand on
the stone and draws power from the earth itself. This skill works
best in underground areas and mountains where the connection to raw
stone is strongest. The amount of spell points restored depends on
the Ranger's wisdom and guild level.
